Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:47.09,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}哭泣时  气馁时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:51.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就要简单地思考后Try Again
